To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private Hammer _hammer;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_hammer = Hammer(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_hammer.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "hammer", _hammer.Current.Value);
}
# In Initialize()
symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
self.hammer = self.Hammer(symbol)

# In OnData()
if self.hammer.IsReady:
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "hammer", self.hammer.Current.Value)
